<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢٨٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3997">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ يُوسُفَ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ </a>وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/676">إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِذَا كَانُوا ثَلَاثَةٌ، فَلَا يَتَنَاجَى اثْنَانِ دُونَ الثَّالِثِ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>